CatDescriptText: The posters in the Shapp Headquarters storefront windows read, "Milton Shapp Governor, A Man You Can Trust".  A market next door has a sign that reads, "Dedication Days, Post Office Dedication, Sunday, April 24th, 3pm".
TitMainTitle: Five men, including one shaking hands with another man, standing in front of campaign headquarters for Milton Shapp for Governor, street no. 806
